International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
[Please note that these reports have been edited to replace "flu-like",
"Norwalk-like", "bug", et alia, with the International Committee on
Taxonomy of Viruses approved designation "Norovirus" for the calicivirus
presumed or confirmed to be responsible for sudden onset viral
gastroenteritis. - Mod.CP]
